        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-03-19 14:08:39.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI approved this merge, but really it does nothing.\n\nFor OpenDaylight based projects to compile correctly, they need to inherit from the OpenDaylight project's parent poms to be sure that the ODL compile tools (e.g. yangtools compiler) are configured correctly and that third party library versions remain consistent.  CCSDK provides parent poms that inherit from the ODL parent poms (to pick up that configuration), and whose contents contain contents of oparent + some additional settings specific to CCSDK",
        "patchset_number": 1
      }
    ]
